{"tid":1662301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"罷食要升級","createTime":"2019-10-18T16:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T16:41:59.000Z","uid":235883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e56e94a37b10b3105ff51d42b61570cb447e02b","tid":1662301,"uid":235883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"#手動傳<br />\n<br />\n自發由今天14/10/2019開始一個行動，凡是商戶門口民建聯、工聯會或是建制派選舉海報一律不光顧！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n#絕不幫襯<br />\n#集結和理非<br />\n#罷賣罷食罷座<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#食兩家茶禮都唔幫襯</span><br />\n重點：<br />\n不光顧之餘，向該店解釋爲何不光顧，等佢知道自己衰乜。"},{"pid":"af67bcffdc6cafef94e2c4aabdfbf8c6c032d0a2","tid":1662301,"uid":330051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4328da9a61a0c1daa6e3cf55d63737bfa676e249","tid":1662301,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:18:45.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n【日常文宣】[推爆佢]本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"36c154aba6ce25cfba4346acaf897188aa1e3fc6","tid":1662301,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T16:20:01.000Z","msg":"Twitter係每日必做的任務<br />\n禁兩個制都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲同我retweet哂去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日國際新聞關香港或者抵制中國事的有：<br />\nDior (向中國道歉，承認台灣係中國）<br />\n<br />\nBlizzard(共雪禁左美國大學隊賽半年，原因係美國大學隊支持Free Hong Kong)<br />\n<br />\nDreamwork（動畫畫九段線，畫出大部分的南海係屬於中國，菲律賓嚴重抗議，荷蘭海牙仲裁已經響2016裁定九段線違反聯合國國際公約，所以Dreamwork 奶共奶到洗緊細路腦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nnba (Lebron James 鬧Morey咩都唔知就亂tweet，大家可以提出任何人都唔應該響普世價值上助紂為虐、自我審查！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你響twitter大海中唔知retweet咩好<br />\ntwitter 組整左個bot<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHe